dependencies:

  * GNU or Intel compilers, GNU Scientific Library, OpenMPI (other implementations may also work), XTC Library (from gromacs.org)

install:

  0. `cd src/jls/`
  
  1. edit main.cpp to your liking (optional)

  2. edit the makefile to match your environment.  see the provided
     makefiles for examples.
  
  3. `make`
  
  there will be a "jls" binary.  that's it.
